organic.title: 477 - Spokane Tribe of Indians
organic.snippet: Spokane Tribal 477 is a tribally operated department with sites in Wellpinit, West End, Ford, and Spokane. 477 offers an array of services.

organic.title: Spokane Tribe of Indians – Improving the lives of our Members
organic.snippet: We are here to improve the lives of members of the Spokane Tribe of Indians. From job opportunities to programs for all ages, we've got something for everyone!
